name: AuthenticatorAttestationResponse
description: The AuthenticatorAttestationResponse interface of the Web Authentication API is returned by CredentialsContainer.create() when a PublicKeyCredential is passed, and provides a cryptographic root of trust for the new key pair that has been generated. This response should be sent to the relying party's server to complete the creation of the credential.

refs.name: Web Authentication: An API for accessing Public Key Credentials - Level 3
